.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There 5 different types of food: peas, papaya, tomato, cauliflower, radish
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: hip-hop, trance, soul, r&b, ambient
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: peasmaster, dunhill, pall-mall, prince, blend
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: dahlia, amaryllis, marigold, daisy, tulip
1. the fan of hip-hop is the person eating tomato
2. the fan of swedish is the person who growsmarigold
3. the fan of trance is the person drinking tea
4. the person eating papaya is on the left of the person eating cauliflower
5. the person eating papaya is the person drinking coffee
6. the pall-mall-smoker is the person who growsamaryllis
7. the person eating radish is the dunhill-smoker
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the fan of r&b is on the far left
10. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia
11. the person who growstulips is on the left or right of the dunhill-smoker
12. the peasmaster-smoker is the person drinking beer
13. the fan of soul is the prince-smoker
14. the fan of r&b is on the left or right of the person eating peas
15. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Food		|    radish	|     peas	|      tomato	|     papaya	|     cauliflower	|
| Music-Genre	|   r&b	|    trance	|    hip-hop	|    soul	|    swedish	|
| Flower		|     dahlia	|    tulip	|     amaryllis	|     daisy	|      marigold	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Cigar		|   dunhill	|    blend	|  pall-mall	|    prince	|   peasmaster	|
